      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "' from ComShinkEvent changed to fit in M2000"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "' event support for Late-Bound objects"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "' low level COM Projekt - by [rm_code] 2005"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "' HOW IT WORKS"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "' An object, wich supports events,"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "' should implement IConnectionPointContainer."
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "' This interface let's you enumerate all"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "' event interfaces."
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "' Once you have the event interface you want,"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "' you can get IConnectionPoint for this interface,"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "' advise your event sink to it, and start"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "' recieving events on it."
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "' If the event interface has IDispatch implemented,"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "' all raised events will go through"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "' IDispatch::Invoke."
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "' And that's what we use:"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "' We just take the first best event interface we"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "' get from IEnumConnectionPoints, create a"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "' event sink which implements IDispatch,"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "' and capture all events through Invoke()."
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
